ing%20a%20Backstreet%20Boys%20concert%20at%20the%20Sphere%20in%20Vegas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anna%20Rahmanan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20August%2C%20I%20took%20a%2048-hour%20break%20from%20motherhood%20to%20see%20the%20Backstreet%20Boys%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELogistics%20and%20maternal%20guilt%20made%20planning%20the%20trip%20tricky%2C%20but%20I%20committed%20to%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20experience%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20self-care%20and%20reclaiming%20joy%20for%20mothers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Backstreet%20Boys%20announced%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftickets%2Fbackstreet-boys-las-vegas-sphere-residency-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELas%20Vegas%20residency%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Sphere%20this%20past%20February%2C%20I%20was%2026%20weeks%20pregnant%20with%20my%20fourth%20kid.%20Within%20minutes%2C%20my%20two%20college%20friends%20with%20whom%20I'd%20spent%20countless%20days%20and%20nights%20belting%20out%20karaoke%20versions%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Call%2C%26quot%3B%20dropped%20the%20news%20into%20our%20group%20chat.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20are%20we%20booking%3F%26quot%3B%20they%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20right%2C%20of%20course.%20We%20had%20to%20go.%20Not%20just%20because%20it%20was%20the%20Backstreet%20Boys%2C%20though%20they%20were%20the%20soundtrack%20to%20so%20many%20of%20our%20college%20and%20post-collegiate%20experiences%2C%20but%20because%20it%20was%20the%20Sphere%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisited-sphere-las-vegas-thought-it-was-incredible-review-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20futuristic%20arena%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20everyone%20was%20buzzing%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20with%20shows%20scheduled%20for%20July%20and%20August%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20be%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20me%20to%20get%20there.%20By%20then%2C%20my%20baby