ding%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20wait%20as%20long%20as%20possible%20to%20see%20if%20anything%20would%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20late%20summer%2C%20however%2C%20it%20seemed%20the%20Backstreet%20Boys%20had%20taken%20over%20my%20algorithm.%20Clips%20of%20the%20show%20flooded%20my%20social%20media%20feeds.%20My%20friends%20kept%20sending%20me%20videos%20of%20fans%20in%20white%2C%20losing%20their%20minds%20at%20the%20Sphere.%20One%20meme%20in%20particular%20lodged%20itself%20in%20my%20brain%3A%20a%20mom%20boarding%20a%20plane%20to%20Vegas%2C%20captioned%2C%20%26quot%3BMe%3A%20a%2040-year-old%20mom%20on%20my%20way%20to%20the%20Baskstreet%20Boys%20concert%20that%20I%20paid%20for%20with%20my%20own%20adult%20money.%20But%20I%20still%20had%20to%20ask%20my%20mom's%20permission%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%20I'd%20never%20felt%20so%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221265%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sphere%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20advertising%20a%20Backstreet%20Boys%20concert%20in%20August%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6941bc0704eda4732f2da03e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20wasn't%20an%20easy%20or%20a%20quick%20decion%20for%20the%20author%2C%20but%20she%20decided%20to%20treat%20herself%20to%2028-hours%20away%20from%20her%20family%20to%20attend%20a%20Backstreet%20Boys%20concert%20at%20the%20Sphere%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anna%20Rahmanan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9eb9596-d213-48af-92e7-a29e1c04be04%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20went%20for%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20I%20cracked.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20ready%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20messaged%20my%20friends.%20Within%20hours%2C%20three%20of%20us%20booked%20a%20round-trip%20ticket%20from%20New%20York's%20JFK%20to%20Harry%20Reid%20International%20Airport%3A%20out%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20back%20on%20the%20red-eye%20Monday%2C%20just%20in%20time%20for%20Tuesday's%20c