en%20it%20truly%20felt%20like%20a%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221582%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20approaching%20the%20Sphere%20in%20Vegas%20before%20a%20Backstreet%20Boys%20concert%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6941abdf04eda4732f2d9e70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221187%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETK%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anna%20Rahmanan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20was%20inside%2C%20when%20Brian%2C%20AJ%2C%20Kevin%2C%20Nick%2C%20and%20Howie%20launched%20into%20%26quot%3BGet%20Down.%26quot%3B%20I%20hadn't%20danced%20like%20that%20in%20so%20long%2C%20and%20neither%20had%2C%20apparently%2C%20the%2020%2C000%20other%20people%20around%20me.%20It%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20concert%3B%20it%20had%20become%20a%20giant%20dance%20party%2C%20an%20unforgettable%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20trip%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20possible%20without%20my%20husband%20holding%20things%20down%20at%20home.%20But%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20also%20think%20of%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20roles%20were%20reversed.%20Before%20leaving%2C%20I%20had%20to%20write%20down%20lists%20and%20make%20calls%20to%20make%20space%20for%20my%20absence%2C%20plus%20pre-cook%20meals%2C%20lay%20out%20outfits%2C%20arrange%20carpools%2C%20pack%20snacks%2C%20and%20orchestrate%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-thankless-random-compliment-has-stuck-with-me-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20small%20details%20of%20family%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20part%20of%20my%20everyday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%20that%20in%20our%20household%2C%20like%20so%20many%20others%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvisble-labor-home-mom-teaches-kids-notice-and-do-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvisible%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20falls%20on%20me%2C%20the%20mother.%20Which%20is%20why%2